cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SI. 

The paper proposes a method for non-parametric estimation of mutual information between random vectors in $\mathbb{R}^d$ based on a bipartite graph. This involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), and data structures (cs.DS). The proposed method also involves randomized Locality Sensitive Hashing (LSH) (cs.AI) and linear programming (cs.SI).
